### Diagnosis API Testing
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5117
@token = YOUR_DOCTOR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Health Check - No authentication required
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/diagnosis/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Test 1: Diagnose with Arabic symptoms (Fever + Cough)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/diagnosis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "patient-123",
  "symptomsText": "المريض عنده سخونية شديدة وكحة مستمرة من يومين"
}

###

### Test 2: Diagnose with Arabic symptoms (Chest pain + Fever + Cough)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/diagnosis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "patient-456",
  "symptomsText": "المريض يشتكي من ألم في الصدر مع سخونية وكحة شديدة"
}

###

### Test 3: Diagnose with English symptoms
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/diagnosis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "patient-789",
  "symptomsText": "Patient has severe headache and dizziness for 3 days"
}

###

### Test 4: Diagnose with mixed Arabic/English symptoms
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/diagnosis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "patient-101",
  "symptomsText": "المريض عنده fever و headache و nausea من امبارح"
}

###

### Test 5: Gastrointestinal symptoms
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/diagnosis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "patient-202",
  "symptomsText": "ألم في البطن مع إسهال وقيء وغثيان"
}

###

### Test 6: Invalid request - Empty symptoms
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/diagnosis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "patient-303",
  "symptomsText": ""
}

###

### Test 7: Invalid request - Missing patient ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/diagnosis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "symptomsText": "المريض عنده سخونية"
}

###

### Test 8: Invalid request - Symptoms too short
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/diagnosis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "patient-404",
  "symptomsText": "سخونية"
}

###

### Test 9: Complex symptoms case
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/diagnosis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "patient-505",
  "symptomsText": "المريض يعاني من سخونية عالية 39 درجة مع كحة جافة وألم في الصدر عند التنفس وضيق في التنفس وصداع شديد"
}

